{"tid":1027880,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一支fuji鏡頭] 35mm f/1.4 定 35mm f/2","createTime":"2019-02-19T05:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T10:11:18.000Z","uid":129959,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"71e5ddcaf5ef5cd78239ce2226c0949ea03d16b6","tid":1027880,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"新手想買第一支定焦鏡，用緊XT-2<br />\nf/1.4就對焦慢，但大部分review都話畫質較好，散景靚<br />\nf/2就平5-7舊水，Weather Resistant，對焦快<br />\n<br />\n我係諗緊對焦快係咪真係好重要？同埋f/1.4係咪真係慢到below average？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個會好d？定係有其他選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdb697bd71dd936ed8863b4eacdf77381031d6b","tid":1027880,"uid":6221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"f1.4"},{"pid":"ecbf6cdb3548c399d1efd16d61795766d1f66228","tid":1027880,"uid":96453,"like":3,"dislike":66,"score":-63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:06:03.000Z","msg":"景<br />\n16.4 <br />\n景 加人<br />\n23.4 <br />\n上半身人<br />\n56.2<br />\n<br />\nxf35(等效53左右)根本垃圾焦距，完全唔wide 但又唔夠遠<br />\nxf35除左平之後，根本無優點"},{"pid":"5399eb061c4f51f3a0f9ff9dfc4175bf0e52fabc","tid":1027880,"uid":218318,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:11:00.000Z","msg":"f2 細支咁多，對焦快好多下，f1.4太慢<br />\n其實好少用到1.4，境深太淺"},{"pid":"f9b6b87090895b01446874b93c3ab45f55af8025","tid":1027880,"uid":176123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"幾點個人見解:<br />\n&gt; 景深方面係有分別 不過唔係要考慮既地方 （f2 9 blades, f1.4 8 blades)<br />\n&gt; f2既優點係有WR 去旅行、天氣唔好既時候方便d<br />\n&gt; 重量分別可有可無<br />\n&gt; f1.4顔色分明度強f2非常多 可以參考下 7:14 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/gj7XIBl9nO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgj7XIBl9nO4&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=d164450f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gj7XIBl9nO4</a><br />\n&gt; f1.4 aperture ring = 垃圾 好易撞郁"},{"pid":"c213d2cd4880529256f3720a80fa8b94b2bce4cf","tid":1027880,"uid":123819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"畫質其實真係唔差太多<br />\n散景 1.4 &gt; f2 就梗啦<br />\n唔洗對焦快/WR 揀 1.4<br />\n要快/WR 就 f2<br />\n<br />\n2支我都用過, 其實好少會下下開到1.4影<br />\n最後放左1.4 同2, 因為要影小朋友, 所以我揀f2"},{"pid":"69c9659fdd44bf3b0c473eefe709cd95850c63e3","tid":1027880,"uid":42700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"f/1.4"},{"pid":"0254b4f0f802132b37848a77646f6235b0d66dff","tid":1027880,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"1.4"},{"pid":"6a00a405db9c76f722bda58d5211a5fb9313b304","tid":1027880,"uid":5996,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"用緊xt3+ 35f2，平d、filter細d平d、又有wr、對焦又快d<br />\n本身都想買1.4，但試鏡果時不斷拉風箱、同埋外對焦+冇wr真係好冇安全感，最後寧願細一級光圈買2<br />\n大光圈下，2既邊緣實過1.4 好多，雖然話如果邊緣係散景實唔實都冇乜所謂，但如果影果樣野係覆蓋幾乎整個畫面，邊緣資訊都好重要"},{"pid":"de352006404bed22137864962cf6251d53782d8f","tid":1027880,"uid":208689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"鍾意35.4<br />\n感覺上影人會比較柔和<br />\n再加大一級光圈"},{"pid":"207aceca274344764701f215448ca9f2c5d24951","tid":1027880,"uid":176123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://alikgriffin.com/fujifilm-35mm-f1-4-vs-35mm-f2-lens-comparison/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Falikgriffin.com%2Ffujifilm-35mm-f1-4-vs-35mm-f2-lens-comparison%2F&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=95cf877e\" target=\"_blank\">https://alikgriffin.com/fujifilm-35mm-f1-4-vs-35mm-f2-lens-comparison/</a><br />\n我覺得呢個comparison 都算全面"},{"pid":"3891aab24bc1d522ff5b4066cf46dcf3d1336b27","tid":1027880,"uid":125612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"富士堆1.4 鏡影黑白好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\